ElyraSQL wire protocol (elyra-wire)

This crate is a first-party fork of opensrv-mysql
(https://github.com/datafuselabs/opensrv), Copyright 2021 Datafuse Labs,
licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

ElyraSQL maintains and extends it as its own MySQL-compatible wire protocol
implementation (native prepared statements, caching_sha2_password, updated TLS
stack). The original Apache-2.0 license and copyright headers are preserved in
the source files; see LICENSE.
